strings: <voice_0x010014F3><se_low>King of tricks: My fever seems to be gone.
<voice_0x010014F4><se_low>King of tricks: Doctors thought something was wrong with the boy, and it was.
<voice_0x010014F5><se_low>King of tricks: I think it is time for a break.
<voice_0x010014F6><se_low>King of tricks: Take care of yourselves my love. I've been told I haven't eaten much since my mother died.
<voice_0x010014F7><se_high>media princess: No, dad, it's all right.
<voice_0x010014F8><se_high>media princess: I wanna stay here until you wake up
<voice_0x010014F9><se_low>King of tricks: If you insist, fine. But watch out kid. This can put you at risk of getting sick.
<voice_0x010014FA><se_low>King of tricks: Yes, because he was very lucky. If I can't find it, I can't even imagine what it could be.
